bugs
----

- eggs crack before they land!

game features
-------------

- a playable game (v1.0)
  - index.html with options for playing standard levels or daily levels
  - sensible system for variants which can be encoded in an ASCII map editor and slopiness
  - parse a level from JSON
  - finish a level
  - remember progress in localstorage
  - repair all the JSON stuff and make it more dynamic 
    - x is a spirit, X is a spirit in earth

- v2 map builder
  - random WxH box filled with stuff
  - has a random exit
  - a tunnel of random length
  - then another WxH random box

